    <!-- Legal disclaimer -->
    <string name="legal_title">Legal notice</string>
    <string name="legal_body">V2X2MAP receives and logs ITS-G5 (5.9 GHz, IEEE 802.11p) radio data from vehicles and infrastructure. Receiving and processing this data is subject to national law — in particular telecommunications regulations, data-protection law and the recording of personal data. Make sure you are entitled to receive (and, where applicable, forward) this radio data in your jurisdiction before using the app. By default this app does not upload data to external servers. By tapping "Accept" you confirm that you take responsibility for compliant use.</string>
